    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A country famous for its starry sight. Amanogawa travels there to find the legendary star.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311180/extras/ad4e6c0742df84e272ecb0fdc848961b.avif?t=1733231662\" width=700 height=174 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About the game</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have a comfortable tourist destination in fantastic tourism that can see night sky. Don't forget to find the stars of legend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you can water the flowers, or play the piano. How about sweet cotton candy?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311180/extras/1363e37bf6f3392109b89b6f6726e855.avif?t=1733231662\" width=800 height=347 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect candies by playing simple mini-games. You can buy costumes or desserts with the candies you get, or watch performances at concert halls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311180/extras/f73e2a54890fb9f9fa4e9e8a315532c8.avif?t=1733231662\" width=800 height=347 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you lonely walking around alone? Take a walk with your rabbit friend.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>There are things like this:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a dreamy visual</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a fairytale story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a cute character</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
